
Row 위젯과 mainAxisAlignment (교재 164~165p)
Widget createS2() {
  return Row(
    mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
    children: List.generate(
      5,
      (index) => Container(
        width: 40,
        height: 40,
        color: Colors.red,
        margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
      ),
    ),
  );
}
 
정렬 방식 실습
Widget createBody() {
  return Column(
    children: [
      createS2(MainAxisAlignment.start),
      createS2(MainAxisAlignment.center),
      createS2(MainAxisAlignment.end),
      createS2(MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly),
      createS2(MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween),
      createS2(MainAxisAlignment.spaceAround),
    ],
  );
}
mainAxisAlignment 값에 따라 자식 위젯의 가로 배치가 달라진다.
옵션	설명
start	왼쪽 정렬
center	가운데 정렬
end	오른쪽 정렬
spaceEvenly	균등 간격
spaceBetween	양끝 고정 + 중간 균등
spaceAround	양끝에 절반 간격
________________________________________
 
 4. CrossAxisAlignment 실습 (교재 166~167p)
Widget createS3(CrossAxisAlignment crossAxisAlignment) {
  return Container(
    height: 100,
    color: Colors.blue,
    child: Row(
      crossAxisAlignment: crossAxisAlignment,
      children: List.generate(
        5,
        (index) => Container(
          width: 40,
          height: 40,
          color: Colors.red,
          margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
        ),
      ),
    ),
  );
}
 
crossAxisAlignment는 세로 정렬(보조축 정렬)을 담당한다.
옵션	설명
start	위쪽 정렬
center	가운데 정렬
end	아래쪽 정렬
stretch	세로로 꽉 채움
________________________________________
 
5. Row와 Column 혼합 사용 (교재 168~169p)
return Row(
  children: [
    createS4(MainAxisAlignment.start),
    createS4(MainAxisAlignment.center),
    createS4(MainAxisAlignment.end),
    createS4(MainAxisAlignment.spaceAround),
    createS4(MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween),
    createS4(MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly),
    createS5(CrossAxisAlignment.start),
    createS5(CrossAxisAlignment.center),
    createS5(CrossAxisAlignment.end),
  ],
);
Column 예시
Widget createS4(MainAxisAlignment mainAxisAlignment) {
  return Column(
    mainAxisAlignment: mainAxisAlignment,
    children: List.generate(
      5,
      (index) => Container(
        width: 40,
        height: 40,
        color: Colors.red,
        margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
      ),
    ),
  );
}
Column + CrossAxisAlignment 예시
Widget createS5(CrossAxisAlignment crossAxisAlignment) {
  return Container(
    width: 100,
    color: Colors.blue,
    margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
    child: Column(
      crossAxisAlignment: crossAxisAlignment,
      children: List.generate(
        5,
        (index) => Container(
          width: 40,
          height: 40,
          color: Colors.red,
          margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
        ),
      ),
    ),
  );
}
________________________________________
 6. Expanded 위젯 (교재 170p)
Widget createS6() {
  return Row(
    mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly,
    children: [
      Expanded(
        child: Container(
          height: 40,
          color: Colors.red,
          margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
        ),
      ),
      ...List.generate(
        4,
        (index) => Container(
          width: 40,
          height: 40,
          color: Colors.red,
          margin: const EdgeInsets.all(5),
        ),
      ),
    ],
  );
}
 
 Expanded는 남은 공간을 flex 비율로 분할한다.
